  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 375°F (190°C).",
    "Slice the ciabatta bread into thin rounds and spread a small amount of diastatic malt syrup on each slice.",
    "Top with balsamic glaze, followed by layers of fresh spinach leaves, grilled zucchini slices, and red bell pepper.",
    "Bake for 10-15 minutes or until the crust is lightly golden and crisp.",
    "Serve warm as a snack."
